These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, family, spy
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, airplane, car
1. the person watching documentary movies is the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | spy | family    |
| Transport     | airplane    | car       | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, paramedic, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the mechanic is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
4. the paramedic is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | mechanic | nurse | paramedic  |
| Sport   | cricket  | skiing  | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, engineer, writer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, soul, d&b
1. the fan of soul is on the far left or far right##3
2. the chef is on the far right##1
3. the engineer is the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | writer | engineer | chef |
| Music-Genre   | indie        | d&b    | soul        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, filmmaking, collecting
3 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, lizard
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
3. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | collecting | filmmaking | puzzles |
| Pet     | rabbit  | turtle    | lizard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, mystery, thriller
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person driving the trike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | romance | thriller |
| Transport     | helicopter   | tram   | trike   |

