.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, classical, hip-hop
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, canadian, pakistani
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the canadian##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | hip-hop    | trance       |
| Nationality   | canadian | pakistani | polish |

