.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, plum, lemon
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating plum is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk        | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk   |
| Food       | lemon | plum | asparagus |

