.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, argentine, pakistani
3 different pets are kept: fish, bird, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
2. the pakistani is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the fish##2
4. the owner of the fish is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | thai | pakistani | argentine |
| Pet           | bird    | guinea-pig    | fish       |

