2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | camping    | writing   | photography |
| Sport   | weightlifting | volleyball | ice-hockey |

