.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, satire, drama
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, classical, soul
1. the fan of classical is in the middle##1
2. the person watching drama movies is between the fan of soul and the fan of pop##2
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of pop##1
4. the fan of soul is the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | drama | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | classical  | soul    |

