.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, almond-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, family, thriller
1. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | cola | milk         |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | family  | fantasy |

 